[ACTIVITY] 課程學習流程
[ACTOR] 學員 -> {specs/actors/學員.md}
[ACTOR] 系統 -> {specs/actors/系統.md}

[INITIAL]
[STEP:1] @學員 {specs/queries/查詢課程內容.feature}
[STEP:2] @學員 {specs/ui/影片播放器.md}
[DECISION:2a] 是否已看過此影片
  [BRANCH:2a:是]
    [STEP:2a.1] @學員 {specs/ui/從上次進度繼續.md}
  [BRANCH:2a:否]
    [STEP:2a.2] @學員 {specs/ui/從頭播放.md}
[MERGE:2a]
[STEP:3] @學員 {specs/ui/影片播放器.md}
[STEP:4] @系統 {specs/commands/更新影片進度.feature}
[FORK:4a]
  [PARALLEL:4a]
    [STEP:4a.1] @系統 {specs/commands/記錄學習行為.feature}
  [PARALLEL:4a]
    [STEP:4a.2] @系統 {specs/commands/更新學習時數.feature}
[JOIN:4a]
[STEP:5] @系統 {specs/queries/檢查課程完成度.feature}
[DECISION:5a] 課程是否全部完成
  [BRANCH:5a:否 -> 1]
  [BRANCH:5a:是]
    [STEP:5a.1] @學員 {specs/ui/完成證書.md}
[MERGE:5a]
[FINAL]
